snippet.title: Descent - Original Trailer (video game)
snippet.description:
This trailer for the original video game "Descent" aired on MTV and other channels back in 1995.  That's right, this game is now more than 15 years old.

Developer: Parallax Software (Now Volition)
Publisher: Interplay Productions
Release Date: March - 1995
